1.00	Al_Ayam_(Bahrain)	Al Ayam (Bahrain)	Al Ayam (The Days) is Bahrain's leading liberal daily newspaper. Owned by the former Information Minister, Nabeel Al Hamer, who today also serves as an advisor to King Hamad, it is generally supports the government while providing a voice for the Kingdom's embattled liberals. In Bahrain's ever expanding newspaper market, the paper faces increased competition from the new Al Watan, which has recruited a number of its senior journalists and has set out to establish itself as Bahrain's newspaper of record.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/8/87/Alayam.gif
